OL,3,COne of world's rarest sharks caught on
OL,4,Ccamera off Welsh coast
OL,6,FOne of the world's rarest sharks has
OL,7,Fbeen captured on camera off the coast
OL,8,Fin west Wales.
OL,10,FAn underwater camera deployed by
OL,11,Fresearchers at The Wildlife Trust of
OL,12,FSouth & West Wales (WTSWW) caught the
OL,13,Fcritically endangered Angelshark on
OL,14,Fthe seabed along Cardigan Bay.
OL,16,FI i's the first time the species has
OL,17,Fbeen seen on film in the area since
OL,18,F2021.
