OL,6,F"We were thrilled to record an
OL,7,FAngelshark in Cardigan Bay, a rare and
OL,8,Fexciting encounter," Dr Sarah Perry,
OL,9,FMarine Conservation and Research
OL,10,FManager at WTSWW, said.
OL,12,F"This sighting comes at a crucial
OL,13,Ftime, as the Senedd and UK Government
OL,14,Fdiscuss a ban on bottom trawling in
OL,15,FMarine Protected Areas.
