OL,6,F"Our Dolphin Diet Detectives project,
OL,7,Ffunded by the Welsh Government through
OL,8,Fthe Nature Networks Fund, uses
OL,9,Funderwater cameras to reveal the
OL,10,Fincredible diversity of life on the
OL,11,Fseabed. These findings highlight the
OL,12,Furgent need to protect these fragile
OL,13,Fhabitats from damaging activities like
OL,14,Fbottom trawling."
