OL,6,FAngelsharks are suffering significant
OL,7,Fdeclines as a result of fishing and
OL,8,Fhabitat degradation. They live on the
OL,9,Fseabed where they are well camouflaged
OL,10,Fto ambush flatfishes, crustaceans and
OL,11,Fmolluscs. But their bottom dwelling
OL,12,Flifestyle makes them vulnerable to
OL,13,Fbeing caught in trawl nets, and along
OL,14,Fwith their slow reproduction rate this
OL,15,Fputs them at a high risk of extinction.
