OL,6,FThe Wildlife Trusts says even Marine
OL,7,FProtected Areas, of which there are
OL,8,F139 in Wales, are not yet fully
OL,9,Fprotected from destructive fishing
OL,10,Factivities such as bottom trawling,
OL,11,Fwhere huge nets and chains are dragged
OL,12,Falong the ocean floor, bulldozing
OL,13,Fanything in their way.
